quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  27,67,Yeh munkireen kehte hain “kya jab hum aur hamare baap dada mitti ho chuke honge to humein waqayi qabaron se nikala jayega?”
  27,68,"Yeh khabrein humko bhi bahut di gayi hain aur pehle hamare aabaa o ajdaad ko bhi di jaati rahi hain, magar yeh bas afsane hi afsane hain jo agle waqton se sunte chale aa rahey hain”"
  27,69,"Kaho, zara zameen mein chal phir kar dekho ke mujreemo ka kya anjaam ho chuka hai"
  27,70,"(Aey Nabi), inke haal par ranjh na karo aur na inki chaalon par dil tangg ho"
  27,71,Woh kehte hain ke “yeh dhamki kab poori hogi agar tum sacchey ho?”
  27,72,"Kaho, kya ajab ke jis azaab ke liye tum jaldi macha rahey ho uska ek hissa tumhare qareeb hi aa laga ho"
  27,73,"Haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb to logon par bada fazal farmane wala hai, magar aksar log shukar nahin karte"
  27,74,Bila shubha tera Rubb khoob jaanta hai jo kuch unke seenay apne andar chupaye huey hain aur jo kuch woh zaahir karte hain
  27,75,Aasmaan o zameen ki koi posheeda cheez aisi nahin hai jo ek wazeh kitaab mein likhi hui maujood na ho
  27,76,Yeh waqia hai ke yeh Quraan bani Israel ko aksar un baaton ki haqeeqat batata hai jin mein woh ikhtilaf rakhte hain
  27,77,Aur yeh hidayat aur rehmat hai iman laney walon ke liye
  27,78,Yaqeenan (isi tarah) tera Rubb in logon ke darmiyan bhi apne hukum se faisla kardega. Aur woh zabardast aur sab kuch jaan-nay wala hai
  27,79,"Pas aey Nabi, Allah par bharosa rakkho, yaqeenan tum sareeh haqq par ho"
  27,80,"Tum murdon ko nahin suna sakte, na un behron tak apni pukar pahuncha sakte ho jo peeth phair kar bhaagey ja rahey hon"
  27,81,Aur na andhon ko raasta bata kar bhatakne se bacha sakte ho. Tum to apni baat unhi logon ko suna sakte ho jo hamari aayat par iman latey hain aur phir farmabardaar ban jatey hain
  27,82,Aur jab hamari baat poori hone ka waqt unpar aa pahunchega to hum unke liye ek jaanwar zameen se nikalenge jo unse kalaam karega ke log hamari aayat par yaqeen nahin karte thay